title: MAYA KEYGEN WINDOWS
description:
Keygens for Autodesk Maya 8,8.5,2008

to install (1) Make a new folder called FLEXLM X:\FLEXLM (X=your drive letter).
           (2) Move awkeygen.exe and aw.dat to root of drive X:\ (X=your drive letter).
           (3) Open FlexLM license utilities - in start menu Autodesk / common utilities.
           (4) Under System Settings tab copy your Ethernet Address.
           (5) Open Aw.dat with notepad/wordpad and replace the words your_host with your ethernet address.
           (6) Open command prompt start>run cmd type cd;\ then type awkeygen.exe aw.dat
           (7) Move aw.dat to FLEXLM folder.
